Description:
 gir1.2-lectordocument-1.5.0 - GObject introspection data for liblectordocument
 gir1.2-lectorview-1.5.0 - GObject introspection data for liblectorview
 lector     - CAFE document viewer
 lector-common - CAFE document viewer (common files)
 liblectordocument-dev - CAFE document rendering library (development files)
 liblectordocument3 - CAFE document rendering library
 liblectorview-dev - CAFE document viewing library (development files)
 liblectorview3 - CAFE document viewing library
Changes:
 lector (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * control:
     - Remove redundant Uploaders field
     - Update Homepage
     - remove obsolete 'Rules-Requires-Root: no'
     - Drop transitional useless package 'gir1.2-lector'
     - Update gir handling
     - Bump to debhelper-compat 13
   * rules:
     - remove obsolete get-orig-source
     - Simplify debian/rules
   * watch: upgrade to version 5
   * drop lector.lintian-overrides
   * lector.install: Adjust to new libexecdir
   * New upstream release
